When I look at the flames, my heart becomes calm... The

\SE[4]Amazing dish...! \!\SE[2]Did you make all of this...!?

\SE[14]Of course, it's only natural! It's a celebration for
the return of Lady Lunaroa...! \SE[13]There's still so much
more that's needed...!!

\SE[4]You should be grateful to Tita, you know? \SE[3]She's
the one who took care of you, a bedridden person, for three
years.

\SE[21]I-It's nothing much...! \!\SE[0]When it comes to Lady
Lunaroa, this is just a piece of cake...!
\SE[2]Tita-chan... Why did you go so far for me...?

\SE[20]No, why... \SE[19]It's because I 'like' you, of
course.

\SE[58] (Didn't you notice... Well, she was sleeping after
all...)

\SE[4]B-By the way, it's unfortunate about Unagi-san, isn't
it? \SE[3]A sudden patient...? They had to leave because of
that...!

\SE[4]Oh, I see... \SE[3]It seems like I also received help
from that person, so I wanted to express my gratitude...

\SE[2]Since Unagi is in the hospital, let's go greet them
when things calm down. \!\SE[75]...By the way.

\SE[52]Isn't it already enough, Laura? \SE[3]You should have
calmed down by now, right?

\SE[28]No, it's still not possible...! I can't possibly show
myself in front of others...!!

\SE[1]Ugh... You really don't have to worry about something
like that at all, you know?

\SE[2]No, Laura. \!\SE[3]I'm already able to cook, so give
up before it gets cold and come out.
\SE[29]Uu... I-I understand... I will make up my mind...
